snippet.title: The Four Color Problem
snippet.description:
Here's a very nice Martin Gardner problem. Take four color pencils and try!
The picture can be downloaded here:
http://www.macoree.com/images/FourColors.png
Next puzzle: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Uo22C9zkeD0
Solution: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=h-UfRyElkzc
Previous puzzle: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=C8G16F8L0OE
Music by Bertrand Laurence:
http://www.bertrandlaurence.com
used with permission.
